710784f-a.text:

710785f-b.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 49th Street
710785f-b.text:
Twelfth Avenue, east side, north from West 49th Street.
View 1 is limited to the 49th to 50th Street frontage.
Note the lunch wagon at the S. E. corner of the latter
point. No. 2 includes the S. E. corner of 49th Street
on the extreme right edge. View 3 is later and shows
the new building line after a slice was taken off of
this side of the Avenue.
June 30, 1930
April 10, 1931
April 15, 1934
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
